{{zh-forms|[[怎么样]]|[[怎么]][[樣]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
Pinyin: zěnme yàng
===Cantonese===
Jyutping: zam<sup>2</sup> mo<sup>1</sup> joeng<sup>6*2</sup>

===Etymology===
From [[怎么]] ("what") + [[樣]] ("type; kind; way")

===Adjective===
#[[how]]; [[what]]; in what way
#: ''[[你]][[覺得]][[那]][[出]][[戲]]'''怎么樣'''? ''
#: ''nǐ juédé nà chū xì '''zěnmeyàng'''?''
#: '''''What''' did you think of that play?''
#: ''[[他]][[還]][[能]][[把]][[我們]]'''怎么樣'''? ''
#: ''tā hái néng bǎ wǒmen '''zěnmeyàng'''?''
#: '''''What''' more can he do to *us*?''
# all that; not much of; not be hard on
#: ''[[我]][[看]][[他]][[的]][[日語]][[水準]][[也]][[並]][[不]]怎么樣''
#: ''wǒ kàn tāde rìyǔ shuǐpíng yě bìngbù '''zěnmeyàng'''''
#: ''In my view, his level of proficiency in Japanese isn't '''all that''' great either''
# [informal] how's it going?

